---
title: Easy Greek-Style Koftas, Haloumi & Shoestring Fries with Cucumber Salad & Garlic Yoghurt
description: These beef koftas are everything you want and more - juicy, tender and flavourful, with fragrant oregano mixed in. Pair them with golden shoestring fries and a crisp salad for the perfect simple accompaniments, then all you need is a tangy yoghurt sauce
to dip it all in!
